reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great little fans for a great price
reviews.reviewText: I love these fans. I use them for my plant greenhouse cabinet. They are quiet, and they hold up well to humidity. Would definitely buy again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Milsbo & Baggebo greenhouse approved
reviews.reviewText: Most of the people that upload videos or TikToks of their cabinets have either these or similar ones, but these are the only ones I’ve tried. I have 3 in each cabinet - 2 pack & 1 pack connected by a USB adapter, and have them plugged in. They’re on 24/7 to provide air flow, and I haven’t noticed them creating any heat. The adjustable speed is nice too - I keep it on the lowest setting.The price is great for what they do, and I plan on putting some up in my Ivar to push air around so I don’t need to leave a regular fan on towards them. These fans are also super easy to install - I just use magnet hooks to hold them in the upper back corners and pointed slightly down. Zip ties would work fine too. They’re small enough to fit anywhere, so I could add more if I ever need to without having to sacrifice any space.Although I’m not using these for my computer, they work great for my plants!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This little fan is seriously mini, like, way smaller than I thought. It's super quiet, but the breeze it gives off is like, tiny too. One thing that bugs me is the wire connecting to the fan is just out there, with no protection or anything – looks like it could easily get damaged.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This product does the job. My boys love their Xbox but those things overheat bad. We bought two of these to cool them down and they work perfectly. The triple speed selection is also a bonus as one needs more flow than the other. Great buy!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very very quiet but moves a lot of air
reviews.reviewText: I bought another fan that was smaller from another company that claimed that theirs was quieter than this one but it was actually very loud had a high-pitched whine couldn't even use it on medium and high because of the noise. This fan is very very quiet you can't hear it on low at a foot away you can barely hear it on medium at a foot or two away and even on high you can hear it maybe five or six feet away and it's mostly just the air that you hear not the motor. This is in a quiet room also. Like library quiet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Quiet but powerful!
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this small fan for my Ikea cabinet/ tabletop greenhouse. It's perfect for this cabinet. The rubber "feet" act as cushion to absorb any vibration and make hanging a breeze. I will be buying more for the other cabinets.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Perfect for my small greenhouse cabinet

reviews.reviewTitle: White fans are not fully white but seem to be good quality
reviews.reviewText: Purchased these for my IKEA MILSBO greenhouse cabinet and I'm yet to set them up, but I've turned them on they are nice and quiet and provide soft, steady air flow.If colour is a concern to you: I'm going for a fully white aesthetic (white cabinet, white lights and cables, planters, etc.) and was disappointed that the fans I received are not fully white as shown in the product images. The fans I received have a black centre circle/logo with white text. I couldn't contact the seller directly to see if the full white fans were available so Amazon was great in dealing with this quickly and compensating me for the misleading product images.
